00:08:12,324 --> 00:08:13,991
我不知道你什么意思
I don't even know what that means.

166
00:08:14,026 --> 00:08:16,060
好吧 我觉得你要剪个头
Well, I think you could use a haircut,

167
00:08:16,094 --> 00:08:18,047
而且我肯定佩内洛普会乐意的
and I'm pretty sure Penelope would appreciate it.

168
00:08:18,048 --> 00:08:19,264
我真的没空
Well, I really don't have time.

169
00:08:19,265 --> 00:08:21,237
事实上你有空 因为你运气不错 
Actually, you do, because luckily, 

170
00:08:21,238 --> 00:08:22,289
我对剪头发很拿手
I am very talented at cutting hair.

171
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:24,502
在高中的时候我经常帮我朋友剪
I used to do all my friends' hair in high school.

172
00:08:24,536 --> 00:08:26,337
这是我众多天赋之一
It's one of my many gifts.

173
00:08:26,371 --> 00:08:28,472
- 但我不想剪啊 - 我才不管
- But I don't want a haircut. - I don't care.

174
00:08:28,507 --> 00:08:30,174
走
Let's go.

175
00:08:30,208 --> 00:08:31,675
好嘞
Okay.

176
00:08:31,709 --> 00:08:33,760
别太短了 好吗? 
Not too short, okay?  

177
00:08:33,761 --> 00:08:36,039
放松 一点都不会痛的
Relax. It's not gonna hurt at all.

178
00:08:36,636 --> 00:08:38,971
嘿 别动
Hey. Stay still.

179
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,722
天哪 这里就像是在蒸桑拿
Man, it's like a sauna in here.

180
00:08:43,756 --> 00:08:45,857
我知道 我一直在叫罗杰修炉子
I know. I keep asking Roger to fix the furnace.

181
00:08:45,891 --> 00:08:50,366
要我去说一下吗? 大家都说我很会烦人的
Want me to bug him for you? I hear I'm very good at bugging people.

182
00:08:50,904 --> 00:08:53,998
- 你说什么? - 我很会烦人
- What did you say? - I'm good at bugging people.

183
00:08:54,033 --> 00:08:55,722
怎么啦?
What?

184
00:08:56,269 --> 00:08:58,103
没事
Nothing.

185
00:08:59,868 --> 00:09:01,835
你还好吧?
You okay?

186
00:09:01,836 --> 00:09:04,331
我很好啊 怎么啦?
Yeah, I'm fine. Why?

187
00:09:04,332 --> 00:09:06,610
你似乎在担心什么事
You seem worried about something.

188
00:09:06,611 --> 00:09:08,746
你有心事的时候就是那个表情
You do that thing with your face when you're worried.

189
00:09:08,781 --> 00:09:10,120
我没什么表情啊  
I don't do a thing with my face.  

190
00:09:10,121 --> 00:09:11,459
你现在就是那个表情
You're doing it right now.

191
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:13,696
我在你后面... 你看不到我的表情
I'm behind you... You can't see my face.

192
00:09:13,722 --> 00:09:16,776
但是我感觉的到 这是我的天赋... 
But I can sense it. It's one of my gifts... 

193
00:09:16,777 --> 00:09:17,625
我很了解你
I can read you like a book.

194
00:09:17,626 --> 00:09:19,142
我不这么认为
I don't think so.

195
00:09:19,592 --> 00:09:21,459
过来
Come here.

196
00:09:34,239 --> 00:09:36,285
各位
Hey, guys.

197
00:09:36,286 --> 00:09:39,822
艾米 你好 我来把这儿收拾干净
Amy. Hi. Let me just help clean up in here.

198
00:09:39,823 --> 00:09:42,691
别 别 不用 我来吧 等会我出去找你们
No, no, no, I got it. I'll just see you out there.

199
00:10:00,297 --> 00:10:04,133
消亡之梦的碎片
Delens somnium meum hominis.

200
00:10:05,369 --> 00:10:08,638
希望这个能有用
Oh, I hope this works.

201
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,660
你还好吗?
You okay?

202
00:10:37,003 --> 00:10:40,705
我想你现在一定感到很困惑
I bet you must be feeling awfully confused right now.

203
00:10:40,739 --> 00:10:42,991
我加入了邪教
I was in a cult.

204
00:10:43,408 --> 00:10:45,845
就要跟阿奇博尔德・布朗宁结婚的时候 
I was about to marry Archibald Browning. 

205
00:10:45,846 --> 00:10:46,523
温迪杀了我
Wendy killed me.

206
00:10:46,524 --> 00:10:49,226
我记得所有这些事 仿佛是昨天发生的
And I remember all of this like it was yesterday.

207
00:10:49,227 --> 00:10:52,016
- 我感到的不仅仅是困惑 - 什么意思?
- Confused doesn't even begin to cover it. - What do you mean?

208
00:10:52,050 --> 00:10:54,385
我知道弗雷娅和我总是年纪轻轻就去世了
I know that Freya and I always die young.

209
00:10:54,419 --> 00:10:58,056
- 你怎么会这么想? - 妈妈!
- Oh, where do you come up with this? - Mom, please!

210
00:10:58,090 --> 00:10:59,927
我看了所有的照片 
I can see all of these pictures, 

211
00:10:59,928 --> 00:11:02,786
但是我们从没有变老过 从没有
but we are never old, ever.

212
00:11:03,396 --> 00:11:07,532
所以我的看法是 我们总是在这个年纪死去
So my theory is, it's because we always die around now.

213
00:11:08,211 --> 00:11:10,452
- 好吧 - 天呐
- Okay. - Oh, my God.

214
00:11:10,453 --> 00:11:12,403
- 是的 你说的对 - 我不敢相信
- Yeah, you're right. - I can't believe this.

215
00:11:12,438 --> 00:11:14,947
- 但是... - 但是什么
- But... - But what?

216
00:11:14,948 --> 00:11:19,398
这次的情况完全不同
This life is completely different.

217
00:11:19,399 --> 00:11:21,862
你们从没有活得这么长过 
You guys have never lived this long before, 

218
00:11:21,863 --> 00:11:23,915
我可以保证你们的安全
and I have kept you safe.

219
00:11:23,950 --> 00:11:25,574
这是我的责任 而且
That's my job, and

220
00:11:25,575 --> 00:11:28,720
你不需要担心这些 因为你的任务
you don't need to worry, because your job

221
00:11:28,721 --> 00:11:33,215
就是尽情地享受生活...
is to live your life to the fullest...

222
00:12:47,031 --> 00:12:48,948
醒来
Wake up.

223
00:12:51,209 --> 00:12:52,607
母亲...
Mother...

224
00:12:54,185 --> 00:12:58,439
我不是你母亲 你认识我 我是雅典娜
I'm not your mother. You knew me as Athena.

225
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:02,276
欢迎回来 英格丽德 我好想你
Welcome back, Ingrid. I missed you.

226
00:13:09,498 --> 00:13:13,033
英格丽德躲着我 弗雷娅要我读她的牌
Ingrid is avoiding me, and Freya asked me to read her cards.

227
00:13:13,034 --> 00:13:14,534
那就去呀
Ugh! So do it.

228
00:13:14,568 --> 00:13:18,104
- 但是我不能说给她听 - 那就别去了
- Well, I can't just read them to her. - Don't do it.

229
00:13:18,139 --> 00:13:21,675
我也不知道该怎么办 温迪
I don't know anymore, Wendy.

230
00:13:21,709 --> 00:13:23,669
如果结果显示她英年早逝了呢?
What if it reveals she dies young?

231
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,995
你不想她这样知道这件事 不是吗?
You don't want her to find out that way, do you?

232
00:13:25,996 --> 00:13:28,216
是的 但是她也许会通过其他方式知道
No, but she might figure it out anyhow.

233
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:31,498
- 嗯 你说的对 - 她有预言的天赋
- Yeah, I guess you're right. - With her gift of premonition.

234
00:13:31,499 --> 00:13:34,383
英格丽德知道了 她有点生气
Ingrid found out. She's mad.

235
00:13:34,384 --> 00:13:37,290
所以她才这么诡异吗?!
Oh. Is that why she's acting so weird?!

236
00:13:37,291 --> 00:13:40,493
当然了 还有其他事
Yeah, among other things.

237
00:13:40,753 --> 00:13:43,221
她也知道了那次是你杀死了她
She also found out about the time you killed her.

238
00:13:43,255 --> 00:13:45,056
什么?
What?

239
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:48,326
我给你这个是让你来浇水的 是吧?
I gave you that so that you could help water, right?

240
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,994
浇水
Aspergo.

241
00:13:50,029 --> 00:13:51,496
她是怎么知道的?
How did she find out?

242
00:13:51,530 --> 00:13:53,933
你认为呢? 她编了一个咒语
How do you think? She cooked up a spell.

243
00:13:55,505 --> 00:13:58,355
关于早逝的事你是怎么跟她说的?
What did you tell her about the whole dying-young thing?

244
00:13:58,356 --> 00:14:01,241
我本想告诉她待在屋里
I wanted to tell her to stay in her room,

245
00:14:01,242 --> 00:14:03,025
关上窗户 让我保护她
shut the blinds, let me keep her safe,

246
00:14:03,026 --> 00:14:07,046
但是却告诉她要活在当下
but instead I told her that she should seize the moment while she can.

247
00:14:07,047 --> 00:14:09,090
当你不知道自己还剩多少时间的时候
When you don't know how much time you have left,

248
00:14:09,091 --> 00:14:12,093
就要抓住现在的每分每秒 不是吗?
you want to make the most of every second, right?

249
00:14:13,479 --> 00:14:15,204
是啊
Yeah.

250
00:14:21,291 --> 00:14:24,360
- 我还活着吗? - 不算是
- Am I alive? - Not quite.

251
00:14:28,432 --> 00:14:30,766
这下好了 现在...
There. Now...

252
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:33,668
这至少可以保持一两天
That should hold, at least for a day or two.

253
00:14:33,703 --> 00:14:35,704
我为什么在这儿?
Why am I here?

254
00:14:35,738 --> 00:14:38,573
你的姨妈温迪偷了
Your aunt Wendy stole something

255
00:14:38,608 --> 00:14:41,743
我父亲阿奇博尔德的东西 也就是你的爱人
from my father Archibald, the man you loved,

256
00:14:41,777 --> 00:14:44,245
你愿意誓死保护的人
and the man you died trying to protect.

257
00:14:44,279 --> 00:14:47,448
- 我要把它拿回来 - 什么东西?
- And I need it back. - What is it?

258
00:14:47,450 --> 00:14:49,885
它叫巨蛇座
It's called serpens clavem.

259
00:14:49,919 --> 00:14:52,587
是一只金色的蛇
It's a golden snake.

260
00:14:52,622 --> 00:14:54,856
它的尾巴看起来像一把钥匙
The tail looks like a key.

261
00:14:54,891 --> 00:14:57,092
我要你把它拿回来
I need you to get it back for me.

262
00:14:57,126 --> 00:14:58,860
你可以完成的
You can do this for me.

263
00:14:58,894 --> 00:15:02,033
我要你设法让温迪单独跟你在一起 
I want you to get Wendy alone, 

264
00:15:02,034 --> 00:15:03,799
说服她把东西交出来
and convince her to give it back.

265
00:15:03,833 --> 00:15:07,637
作为回报 你可以杀了你姨妈
In return, you can kill your aunt,

266
00:15:07,671 --> 00:15:11,407
就像多年前她杀了你一样
the one who murdered you all those years ago.

267
00:15:21,812 --> 00:15:23,231
嗨 利奥
Hi, Leo.

268
00:15:23,951 --> 00:15:26,724
你在这儿做什么? 你怎么知道我在这儿?
What are you doing here? How did you even find me?

269
00:15:26,758 --> 00:15:29,127
我自有我的办法
I have my ways.

270
00:15:29,161 --> 00:15:34,157
我最近一直在想你 很想你
Um, I've been thinking about you lately, a lot, actually.

271
00:15:34,178 --> 00:15:36,980
搞笑 自从你扮成我的邻居 睡了我
That's funny, seeing as how I never heard from you again

272
00:15:37,014 --> 00:15:38,714
还偷了我最自豪的蝴蝶以后
after you pretended to be my neighbor,

273
00:15:38,749 --> 00:15:41,083
我好像再也没有收到过你的消息
slept with me, and then, stole my prized butterfly.

274
00:15:41,118 --> 00:15:42,985
那只猫真是你的吗?
Was that even really your cat?

275
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:44,920
那只小猫绝对是我的
Oh, that little kitty is very much mine.

276
00:15:46,298 --> 00:15:49,792
听着 我... 我真的想打电话跟你道歉
Listen, I... I... I really did mean to call and apologize.

277
00:15:49,793 --> 00:15:52,785
你拿我的喜马拉雅皇冠蝶做了什么?
So what did you do with the Himalayan Stamped Crown you took from me?

278
00:15:52,786 --> 00:15:54,710
你在易贝上把它卖了吗?  
You sell it on eBay?  

279
00:15:54,711 --> 00:15:55,598
不 我没有卖
No, I didn't sell it.

280
00:15:55,633 --> 00:15:58,001
我真的需要它
I really needed it.

281
00:15:58,035 --> 00:15:59,736
而且我还不能解释原因
And... and I can't explain why.

282
00:15:59,770 --> 00:16:01,504
好吧 听着
All right, look,

283
00:16:01,538 --> 00:16:03,705
我很感激你营造的整个神秘的氛围
I appreciate the whole mysterious vibe thing.

284
00:16:03,739 --> 00:16:05,774
我也肯定有人喜欢这种感觉
I'm sure it works on some guys.

285
00:16:05,808 --> 00:16:08,777
只是我现在不想浪费时间去琢磨清楚
I just don't have the time to figure you out right now.

286
00:16:08,811 --> 00:16:11,671
好吗? 我很忙
Okay? I'm busy.

287
00:16:11,672 --> 00:16:14,170
等等 等等 等等 对不起
Okay, wait, wait, wait. Sorry. Okay.

288
00:16:14,316 --> 00:16:15,784
对不起
I'm sorry.

289
00:16:15,818 --> 00:16:19,021
你说的很对 我的确... 的确对你撒谎了
What you said was right. I did... I did lie to you.

290
00:16:19,055 --> 00:16:22,357
的确... 利用了你 我心里很愧疚
I did... use you, and I feel terrible about it.

291
00:16:23,799 --> 00:16:27,317
你也许不想琢磨我 但是我想琢磨你
You may not want to figure me out, but I want to figure you out.

292
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:30,317
我们第一次见面的时候 有一种感觉
When we first met, there was this connection.

293
00:16:30,318 --> 00:16:33,099
我们之间有火花
A spark between us.

294
00:16:34,070 --> 00:16:36,438
而且我想继续发展下去
And I want to get to the bottom of it.

295
00:16:37,231 --> 00:16:38,974
真的吗?
You do?

296
00:16:39,748 --> 00:16:42,712
我姐姐今天对我说了一些很有意义的话
My sister said something to me today that made a lot of sense.

297
00:16:42,746 --> 00:16:44,818
抓住机会享受生活
You got to grab life while you can.

298
00:16:44,819 --> 00:16:47,621
谁知道我们还有几条命... 我的意思是
Who knows how many lives... I mean, years...

299
00:16:47,852 --> 00:16:50,220
还能活几年?
We all have left?

300
00:16:50,254 --> 00:16:53,726
听着 我不是外面那种玩玩而已的人
Look, I'm not in the market for someone who plays games.

301
00:16:53,727 --> 00:16:56,361
我知道 我知道 我真的知道
I get it. I get it, I do.

302
00:16:56,826 --> 00:16:59,762
再给我一次机会吧?
Just give me another chance?

303
00:16:59,796 --> 00:17:01,564
一起去吃午餐吧
Let's go to lunch.

304
00:17:01,598 --> 00:17:05,101
我发誓 我不是玩玩而已
There will be no games, I swear.

305
00:17:06,373 --> 00:17:08,597
除非你想玩点什么
I mean, unless you want to play them.

306
00:17:26,947 --> 00:17:30,395
你真是... 太慷慨了 亲爱的
Oh. Oh, you're... Mmm... So generous, darling.

307
00:17:30,396 --> 00:17:33,231
多谢你能来 爱你
Oh, thank you so much for coming. Love you.

308
00:17:33,266 --> 00:17:36,034
我很快就回来 你好
I'll be right back. Oh, hello.

309
00:17:49,330 --> 00:17:51,826
英格丽德? 你在这儿呀 
Ingrid? Here you are. 

310
00:17:51,827 --> 00:17:52,866
你好 乔治
Hey, George.

311
00:17:55,225 --> 00:17:56,303
你好吗?  
How are you?  

312
00:17:56,304 --> 00:17:58,639
很好 你今天能来真是太好了
Good. It was nice of you to come today.

313
00:17:58,673 --> 00:18:00,207
当然了
Oh, of course.

314
00:18:00,242 --> 00:18:02,910
我在以我的方式支持图书馆的工作
I try to support the library in any way I can.

315
00:18:02,945 --> 00:18:06,786
当然了 也在... 支持你
And, uh... Support you, obviously.

316
00:18:06,787 --> 00:18:08,649
多谢
I appreciate that.

317
00:18:09,895 --> 00:18:11,575
- 你好啊 - 你好
- Hey, you. - Hey.

318
00:18:11,576 --> 00:18:13,777
- 开心吗? - 你开玩笑吧?
- You having a good time? - Are you kidding me?

319
00:18:13,778 --> 00:18:15,688
这是我在图书馆过得最开心的一次
This is the most fun I've ever had in a library.

320
00:18:15,689 --> 00:18:16,946
是吗?
Is it?

321
00:18:16,981 --> 00:18:19,216
我有一个让我们更开心的想法
Well, I know a way we can have even more fun.

322
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:20,784
真的吗?
Oh, really?

323
00:18:20,818 --> 00:18:22,453
我们去伦敦吧
Let's go to London.

324
00:18:23,382 --> 00:18:24,882
什么? 就这样吗?
What? Just like that?

325
00:18:24,883 --> 00:18:27,459
你就这样掰掰手指头 我们就要去伦敦了吗?
You're just gonna snap your fingers, and we're gonna go to London?

326
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:29,475
是的 明天怎么样? 
Yup. How about tomorrow?  

327
00:18:29,476 --> 00:18:30,886
你是认真的吗?
Are you serious?

328
00:18:30,887 --> 00:18:35,251
我被邀请两天后在英国的医学会议上做演讲
I got invited to speak at a medical conference in England in two days.

329
00:18:35,297 --> 00:18:37,598
听着 我知道这有点急 你会去吗?
Look, I know it's last minute but, are you in?

330
00:18:37,633 --> 00:18:40,173
当然去了
Yes, of course I am.

331
00:18:40,174 --> 00:18:42,177
有时候你可能得一个人待着...
You might be on your own for some of it, be...

332
00:18:42,178 --> 00:18:43,545
我是说 我估计...
I mean, I assume you just...

333
00:18:43,546 --> 00:18:44,871
你不愿意一整天听我讲
You know, you don't want to watch me speak 

334
00:18:44,872 --> 00:18:46,087
第三世界接种疫苗什么的
about third world vaccinations all day.

335
00:18:46,088 --> 00:18:49,148
无意冒犯 我想我能找到事做
No offense, I think I can fill my time.

336
00:18:49,149 --> 00:18:52,072
不敢相信我就要在我的护照上盖一个章了
