And when you come back to life, I'll kill you again, as many times as it takes.

509
00:29:06,152 --> 00:29:09,654
英格丽德 等等 我们...
Ingrid, wait. We... we...

510
00:29:11,324 --> 00:29:13,558
我不小心杀了你
I killed you by mistake.

511
00:29:13,593 --> 00:29:16,628
我还是你姨妈
I'm still your aunt.

512
00:29:16,662 --> 00:29:20,331
你还是我的侄女 这不是真正的你
You're still my niece. This isn't who you are.

513
00:29:22,667 --> 00:29:26,735
实际上 我觉得这才是真正的我
Actually, I think this is exactly who I am.

514
00:29:26,769 --> 00:29:28,236
不
No.

515
00:29:28,271 --> 00:29:30,004
夺命掏心
Acidum adere!

516
00:29:40,038 --> 00:29:41,658
英格丽德?
Ingrid?

517
00:29:50,264 --> 00:29:53,300
- 不 妈妈 不要 - 你不是我女儿
- No, mom, please don't. - You're not my daughter.

518
00:29:53,334 --> 00:29:55,674
看着我的眼睛 你知道我是谁
Look in my eyes; You know who I am.

519
00:29:55,684 --> 00:29:57,418
我是英格丽德啊
I'm Ingrid.

520
00:29:58,806 --> 00:30:02,210
我们等会再聊这个
Okay, we'll talk about this later.

521
00:30:04,613 --> 00:30:07,482
我们先带你姨妈离开这里
Let's get your aunt and get her out of here.

522
00:30:08,651 --> 00:30:10,019
恢复!
Reverte!

523
00:30:15,524 --> 00:30:19,861
化为灰烬
Reverte ad vestrum priorem statum.

524
00:30:19,895 --> 00:30:22,097
可你不杀人的啊
But you don't kill people.

525
00:30:22,131 --> 00:30:24,267
你已经死了
You were already dead.

526
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:51,211
- 这么说不是假冒者干的? - 不是
- So it wasn't the shifter? - No.

527
00:30:52,105 --> 00:30:54,507
是另一个很久以前的敌人
It was another enemy from a long time ago,

528
00:30:54,541 --> 00:30:56,676
我猜 是假冒者派来的
I assume, sent by the shifter.

529
00:30:56,711 --> 00:31:00,591
- 谁 什么敌人? - 你不知道
- Who, what enemy? - No one you'd know about.

530
00:31:01,649 --> 00:31:04,685
我已经疗好了她的烧伤 她会好起来的
I've healed her burns, so she's going to be okay.

531
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,454
现在我们只能等
All we can do now is wait.

532
00:31:08,662 --> 00:31:10,787
达什要一个人去伦敦
Dash is going to London without me,

533
00:31:10,788 --> 00:31:13,107
我甚至不知道他还想不想娶我
and I don't even know if he still wants to marry me.

534
00:31:14,095 --> 00:31:18,706
- 亲爱的 怎么了? - 他发现了
- Sweetie, what happened? - He found out.

535
00:31:19,333 --> 00:31:21,702
我就知道会这样的
I knew it was gonna happen.

536
00:31:21,736 --> 00:31:23,904
我只是... 自从我发现自己的身份以来
I just... ever since I found out what I am,

537
00:31:23,939 --> 00:31:26,151
我的直觉变得越来越强烈
my intuition just keeps getting

538
00:31:26,152 --> 00:31:30,477
而且我 我需要更加信任自己
stronger and stronger, and I, I need to trust myself more.

539
00:31:30,512 --> 00:31:33,581
- 很抱歉 弗雷娅 - 达什发现什么了?
- I'm so sorry, Freya. - Dash found out about what?

540
00:31:33,615 --> 00:31:36,183
我和基利安的事 我们接吻了
About Killian and me. We kissed.

541
00:31:36,217 --> 00:31:39,834
- 就在她的订婚宴会上 - 那是个错误!
- At her engagement party. - It was a mistake!

542
00:31:39,835 --> 00:31:41,899
那是我这辈子最大的错误
The biggest mistake of my entire life.

543
00:31:41,907 --> 00:31:46,460
- 因为我就是个坏人 - 你不是坏人
- Because I'm a terrible person. - You're not a terrible person.

544
00:31:46,494 --> 00:31:49,363
人都免不了犯错
People make mistakes.

545
00:31:49,397 --> 00:31:51,332
可不能犯这种错误 妈妈
Not like this, mom.

546
00:31:51,366 --> 00:31:54,201
相信我吧 我犯的错误更多 更严重
Oh, believe me, I've done much, much worse.

547
00:31:54,236 --> 00:31:57,872
我觉得达什离开是件好事
I think it's good that Dash went away.

548
00:31:57,907 --> 00:32:01,443
这样他就有机会一个人想想他怎么会这么爱你
It'll give him some alone time to remember why he loves you so much.

549
00:32:01,477 --> 00:32:04,780
- 你真的这么认为? - 当然
- You really think that? - Definitely.

550
00:32:04,814 --> 00:32:07,850
我们为什么要看温迪姨妈睡觉呢?
Why are we watching aunt Wendy sleep?

551
00:32:07,884 --> 00:32:09,901
她不是在睡觉 她死了 
She's not asleep, she's dead. 

552
00:32:09,902 --> 00:32:11,186
天哪 又死了?
Oh, my God, again?

553
00:32:11,221 --> 00:32:13,275
没事的
It's okay.

554
00:32:13,415 --> 00:32:15,125
她不会死很久的
She won't be long now.

555
00:32:17,061 --> 00:32:18,461
天哪
Oh, God.

556
00:32:18,495 --> 00:32:20,071
这一直不见好
Oh, that never gets any better.

557
00:32:20,072 --> 00:32:23,066
欢迎回来... 很高兴看见你又活过来了
Welcome back... it's nice to see you breathing again.

558
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:26,236
好的 大家都在呢 我错过了什么?
Okay, so we're all here. What did I miss?

559
00:32:26,670 --> 00:32:31,667
你被杀了 然后 一个叫利奥的朋友来看你了
You got killed, um, and, a friend named Leo stopped by, looking for you.

560
00:32:32,668 --> 00:32:36,213
貌似很关心的样子 貌似有点喜欢你
Seemed concerned, seemed to like you.

561
00:32:37,282 --> 00:32:40,554
我猜你听了我的话 对吧?
I guess you took my advice, huh?

562
00:32:40,555 --> 00:32:42,253
嗯 有点吧
Yeah, a little bit.

563
00:32:42,288 --> 00:32:44,989
- 好啦 来吧 姑娘们 - 好
- All right, come on, girls. - Yeah.

564
00:32:45,024 --> 00:32:47,691
我们来让温迪恢复能量
Let's let Wendy get her strength back.

565
00:32:47,726 --> 00:32:48,759
- 英格丽德 - 在呢
- Ingrid. - Yeah.

566
00:32:48,793 --> 00:32:51,228
- 我能跟你说句话吗? - 当然
- Can I talk to you for a second? - Of course.

567
00:32:51,263 --> 00:32:55,066
那我们没事啦? 我是说 我们扯平了?
So we're okay? I mean, we're even now?

568
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:56,300
你什么意思?
What do you mean?

569
00:32:56,301 --> 00:32:58,936
你妈妈没告诉你吗?
Oh, your mom didn't tell you?

570
00:32:58,971 --> 00:33:02,819
你杀了我 当然 我是说 1906年的你
You killed me. Oh, I mean, you know, the you from 1906.

571
00:33:02,820 --> 00:33:04,083
什么?
What?

572
00:33:04,084 --> 00:33:06,677
假冒者教唆你... 以前的你...
The shifter reanimated you... the old you...

573
00:33:06,712 --> 00:33:08,713
然后让你来找我报仇
And sent you after me for revenge.

574
00:33:08,748 --> 00:33:11,049
天哪 我...
Oh, my God, I'm...

575
00:33:11,083 --> 00:33:13,551
那 以前的我现在在哪里?
So, where is old me now?

576
00:33:14,186 --> 00:33:15,756
嗯 我也不知道
Uh, um, I'm not sure.

577
00:33:15,757 --> 00:33:18,790
你得问问你妈妈 不过我确定她已经搞定了
You have to ask your mom about that, but I'm sure she took care of it.

578
00:33:18,824 --> 00:33:22,360
- 对不起 - 没事的 不是你的错
- I'm so sorry. - No, it's okay, it wasn't you.

579
00:33:22,394 --> 00:33:26,480
不 就是我 她干什么 我也有责任
Yes, it was me. I mean, whatever she did, I'm capable of.

580
00:33:26,481 --> 00:33:27,836
我们是一样的  
We're the same person.  

581
00:33:27,837 --> 00:33:29,700
不 亲爱的 不是这样的
No, honey, it doesn't work like that.

582
00:33:29,735 --> 00:33:31,602
所有的生命都完全不同
Every life is completely different.

583
00:33:31,636 --> 00:33:33,453
只是生命终结的时间不同罢了  
Except every life ends about now.  

584
00:33:33,454 --> 00:33:35,331
这可未必
Not necessarily.

585
00:33:35,332 --> 00:33:37,119
要是历史能暗示什么就好了
If history is any indication.  

586
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:39,233
历史也可能改变的 我看见了
History can change; I've seen it.

587
00:33:40,402 --> 00:33:43,171
感觉很怪
It just feels like impossible odds.

588
00:33:43,205 --> 00:33:46,841
我是说 自从我发现自己是女巫以来...
I mean, ever since I discovered what I am...

589
00:33:46,876 --> 00:33:49,711
我就不断收到一些坏消息
It's been an endless parade of bad news.

590
00:33:51,380 --> 00:33:54,116
感觉好像我不知道自己是谁了一样
I feel like I don't know who I am anymore.

591
00:33:54,828 --> 00:33:58,148
要是有什么不同的话 我更了解你了
Well, if it makes any difference, I know who you are.

592
00:33:58,666 --> 00:34:01,567
你有一颗善良的心
You have such a good heart.

593
00:34:01,584 --> 00:34:04,486
你是迄今为止我最喜欢的英格丽德
You're my favorite Ingrid yet.

594
00:34:06,094 --> 00:34:08,262
谢谢
Thank you.

595
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:13,015
- 我爱你 宝贝儿 - 我也爱你
- I love you, sweetie. - I love you, too.

596
00:34:17,606 --> 00:34:20,740
- 还以为你回家了呢 - 我来帮忙清查
- Thought you went home. - Here to help with inventory.

597
00:34:20,775 --> 00:34:24,444
- 天哪 这里好热 - 罗杰不想修火炉
- Man, is it hot in here. - Roger refuses to fix the furnace.

598
00:34:24,478 --> 00:34:26,196
我不停地拿这件事烦他 
I keep bugging him about it. 

599
00:34:26,197 --> 00:34:27,447
想让我去烦他吗?
Want me to bug him?

600
00:34:27,481 --> 00:34:29,683
有人说我特别擅长烦别人
I've been told I'm very good at bugging people.

601
00:34:32,119 --> 00:34:34,087
你得走了
You have to go.

602
00:34:34,121 --> 00:34:36,056
什么?
What?

603
00:34:36,090 --> 00:34:40,995
这是个梦... 是我最后一次梦见你
This is a dream... the last dream I'll have about you.

604
00:34:41,029 --> 00:34:44,331
- 再见了 - 等等 不 你不能
- I'm saying good-bye. - Wait, no, you can't.

605
00:34:44,365 --> 00:34:45,899
弗雷娅 听我说
Freya, listen to me.

606
00:34:45,934 --> 00:34:47,426
这一切都不是你想的那样  
None of this is what you think.  

607
00:34:47,427 --> 00:34:48,116
再见 基利安
Bye, Killian.

608
00:35:13,729 --> 00:35:16,130
嘿 你醒了
Hey, you're up.

609
00:35:16,165 --> 00:35:18,430
- 嘿 - 我做了件正确的事
- Hey. - Well, I did something right.

610
00:35:18,431 --> 00:35:20,528
我念的那个咒语起作用了 
The spell I did worked. 

611
00:35:20,529 --> 00:35:22,800
我想我再也不会梦见基利安了
I think I'm finally done dreaming of Killian.

612
00:35:23,137 --> 00:35:26,331
- 你在干什么? - 弗雷娅 坐下
- What are you doing? - Freya, sit down.

613
00:35:29,743 --> 00:35:33,113
我曾经规定再也不给你们两个占卜了
I made a rule that I would never deal the deck for you girls.

614
00:35:33,147 --> 00:35:34,781
我觉得这是自找麻烦
I think it's asking for problems,

615
00:35:34,815 --> 00:35:37,184
不过我知道你很困惑
but I know you're confused

616
00:35:37,218 --> 00:35:41,488
很好奇 所以我给你做了
and curious, so I did it for you.

617
00:35:41,523 --> 00:35:44,706
- 它说什么? - 很复杂
- Well, what does it say? - It's complicated.

618
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:48,061
比我想象中还要复杂
It's more complicated than I realized.

619
00:35:48,095 --> 00:35:50,911
它有说我和达什将来会怎样吗?
Does it say something about my future with Dash?

620
00:35:50,919 --> 00:35:52,887
我们还会结婚吗?
Are we still getting married?

621
00:35:52,921 --> 00:35:54,622
我不知道会发生什么事
I don't know what will happen.

622
00:35:54,656 --> 00:35:58,334
未来被包在里面
There's a shroud around the future

623
00:35:58,483 --> 00:36:02,296
因为你还没有做决定
because your choice isn't yet made.

624
00:36:02,331 --> 00:36:03,631
什么?
What?

625
00:36:03,665 --> 00:36:06,134
这就是你
This is you

626
00:36:06,168 --> 00:36:10,905
你是一切的中心 被爱和家人包围
in the center of everything, surrounded by love and family.

627
00:36:10,906 --> 00:36:12,291
这才是问题
This is the problem.

628
00:36:12,292 --> 00:36:15,843
什么 是骗子和皇帝吗?
What, the trickster and the emperor?

629
00:36:15,877 --> 00:36:17,511
他们是镜子的两面 
They're mirror images, they're often

630
00:36:17,546 --> 00:36:20,914
经常以兄弟存在... 一个黑暗 一个光明
depicted as brothers... One dark, one light.

631
00:36:20,949 --> 00:36:23,183
这么说一个是达什一个是基利安?
So one is Dash and one is Killian?

632
00:36:23,218 --> 00:36:28,155
还有 根据牌面 他们分开了你的心
Mm-hmm, and, according to the cards, they divide your heart.

633
00:36:28,189 --> 00:36:31,425
那 基利安肯定是黑暗面 对吧?
Well, Killian is obviously the dark one, right?

634
00:36:31,459 --> 00:36:34,494
骗子可能是任何一个
The trickster could be either.

635
00:36:34,529 --> 00:36:37,764
他可能是化妆成光明的黑暗
He could be dark masquerading as light.

636
00:36:37,799 --> 00:36:40,434
这就是他干的事... 他让你困惑
That's what he does... He confuses you.

637
00:36:40,468 --> 00:36:43,170
这是什么意思?
What does that even mean?

638
00:36:43,204 --> 00:36:48,056
根据牌面 你会爱上他们两个
According to the cards, you will love them both.

639
00:36:48,564 --> 00:36:50,887
你必须要做个决定
You have a choice to make.

640
00:36:50,888 --> 00:36:55,883
一个是你的灵魂伴侣 一个是你的冤家
One man is your soul mate, the other man's your destroyer.

641
00:36:56,385 --> 00:37:00,155
你的选择将会决定你的命运
Whoever you choose will decide your fate.

642
00:37:06,493 --> 00:37:09,629
- 终于好了 - 什么?
- Oh, finally. - What?

643
00:37:09,991 --> 00:37:12,960
我一活过来就等着跟你说话
I've been wanting to talk to you since I came back to life,

644
00:37:12,961 --> 00:37:16,035
可我不想当着姑娘们的面说
but I didn't want to say anything in front of the girls.

645
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:17,203
为什么?
Why?

646
00:37:17,238 --> 00:37:21,041
知道吗? 我可以喝一杯
You know what? I could use a drink.

647
00:37:24,838 --> 00:37:26,838
所以呢...
So...

648
00:37:27,966 --> 00:37:31,318
所以 自从你第一次遇到危险
So, you know, ever since I had the first vision of you being in danger,

649
00:37:31,352 --> 00:37:35,316
我们就在努力寻找假冒者和他的目的 对吗?
we've been trying to figure out who the shifter is and what they want, right?

650
00:37:35,317 --> 00:37:39,593
你是说除了毁掉我们以外?
You mean aside from destroying us?

651
00:37:40,742 --> 00:37:43,243
我还不知道假冒者是谁
Well, I still don't know who the shifter is,

652
00:37:43,244 --> 00:37:45,358
不过我想我知道他们的目的了 
but I think I know what they want, 

653
00:37:45,359 --> 00:37:46,567
这可不是好消息
and it's not good news.

654
00:37:47,645 --> 00:37:49,580
那 他们什么目的?
So, what is it?

655
00:37:50,713 --> 00:37:54,397
死去的英格丽德不停地要巨蛇座...
Dead Ingrid kept asking for the serpens clavem...

656
00:37:54,431 --> 00:37:56,199
那条金蛇
The golden snake.

657
00:37:56,632 --> 00:37:58,843
- 真的吗...? - 对
- Really...? - Yeah.

658
00:38:00,704 --> 00:38:02,672
那她为什么要问你呢?
Well, why is she asking you?

659
00:38:02,706 --> 00:38:05,241
我不知道 她以为是我从阿奇博尔德那儿偷的
I don't know, she thought I stole it from Archibald,

660
00:38:05,275 --> 00:38:08,711
我一直告诉她那东西被毁掉了 可她不相信我
and I kept telling her that it was destroyed, and she didn't believe me.

661
00:38:08,746 --> 00:38:10,513
是被毁掉了 对吧?
It was destroyed, right?

662
00:38:10,548 --> 00:38:12,182
是啊 当然
Yes, of course.

663
00:38:12,309 --> 00:38:14,477
你确定吗?
Are you sure?

664
00:38:15,977 --> 00:38:17,836
我只是随便说说 要是你错了呢?
I'm just saying, what if you're wrong?

665
00:38:17,837 --> 00:38:19,390
要是它还在外面
What if it's still out there

666
00:38:19,391 --> 00:38:22,025
假冒者得到它并且打开入口呢?
and the shifter gets a hold of it and opens the portal?

667
00:38:22,059 --> 00:38:24,327
钥匙已经不存在了
The key no longer exists.

668
00:38:24,361 --> 00:38:25,828
我亲眼看见它被毁了
I saw it get destroyed.

669
00:38:25,863 --> 00:38:30,533
没有人能打开那个入口了
No one's opening that portal ever again.

670
00:38:30,568 --> 00:38:32,430
好吧 不过它的分支...
Okay, but the ramus mortium...

671
00:38:32,454 --> 00:38:35,139
正在入口附近的地下墓穴里生长
It was growing in the catacombs near the entrance.

672
00:38:35,140 --> 00:38:38,595
这不仅仅是巧合 对吗?
I think that's more than a coincidence, right?

673
00:38:38,976 --> 00:38:43,380
没有钥匙没有人能打开那扇门
No one can open that door without the key.

674
00:38:43,414 --> 00:38:45,187
钥匙已经不见了
The key is gone.

675
00:38:45,188 --> 00:38:48,448
温迪 别再担心了
Wendy, stop worrying.

676
00:38:49,620 --> 00:38:52,055
好吧 要担心的事还多着呢
Well, it's a lot to worry about.

677
00:38:55,393 --> 00:38:57,728
什么?
What?

678
00:39:00,632 --> 00:39:02,799
